		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Note also that the results you get from $0D on a particular TV can depend on the overall layout of the picture, so it's hard to test &quot;what exactly happens&quot;. For example, on my TV some screens in The Immortal (uses $0D) were shaky and some were OK.

		

